1. **Analyze and Describe the Main Target Image:**

   The main image shows two structures. The larger structure has 7 blocks. One is a tall, rectangular block (possibly a tower), supported by 2 large orange cylindrical blocks. A small, orange triangular block sits below the tower. There is a smaller structure composed of a triangular orange block and a small, light-green block, positioned diagonally on top of the triangular orange block.

      * Block 6 (Yellow Rectangular Tall)
      * Block 9 (Yellow Semi-Circle)
      * Block 11 (Orange Cylinder)
